{"tid":1447914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」星期一1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:17:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T02:39:22.000Z","uid":210495,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4801127f7be66c7b0b22353583827148bfe11d2f","tid":1447914,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:17:15.000Z","msg":"無時間文宣<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=6RyWY35l7oH3ui7gcEo%2FTGHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=dbdd1b29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=6RyWY35l7oH3ui7gcEo%2FTGHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=00e6f664\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"f1288e006dda0bf143f12d8f60c657159594d1be","tid":1447914,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:24:36.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"de404d86a277efa4c4f210af940b0d2353fcf2db","tid":1447914,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:25:29.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"00897ee0926f942da55c5ead5e1fd71fe931825c","tid":1447914,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:26:36.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a0d995c2ab289196d9383631776386253bf76122","tid":1447914,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:30:49.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"3a0deb8912dfda95f825f19f98445c9d525fe42c","tid":1447914,"uid":148152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:31:56.000Z","msg